“As a student/user, I want to create an account and log in to the system so that I can access the system”.
“As an admin, I want to log into the system so that I can manage the schedule”.
View doctor:
“As a student/user, I want to view the list of available doctors so that I can see their specialties and information before booking.”
Book appointment:
“As a student/user, I want to book an appointment with a doctor so that I can schedule a time that works for me to visit the clinic.”
View my appointment:
“As a student/user, I want to view my scheduled appointments so that I can see when and where my appointments are.”
Cancel booking:
“As a student/user, I want to cancel my appointment so that I can free up the appointment slot if my plans change.”
View profile:
“As a student/user, I want to view and manage my profile information so that I can keep my personal details up to date.”
Manage schedule:
“As an Admin, I want to manage available time slots and doctor availability to ensure the schedule is up to date.”
